## Directory Structure
```
└── third_party/            # Directory containing all the third-party implementations
    ├── README.md
    ├── OpenNE/                 # OpenNE library for graph embeddings (https://github.com/thunlp/OpenNE)
    ├── vdist2vec/              # Vdist2vec implementation in TF (https://github.com/alvinzhaowei/vdist2vec)
    ├── ndist2vec/              # Ndist2vec implementation in TF (https://figshare.com/articles/dataset/ndist2vec/20238813/1)
    ├── other_runtimes/         # Misc scripts for comparing runtimes in TF, PyTorch, LibTorch, etc.
    └── ...
```
